# LIN YOUNG AI-readable Portfolio Website

A static personal website for GitHub Pages, built for humans, search engines, and AI systems.

## How to publish on GitHub Pages

1. Create a new GitHub repository.
2. Upload all files in this folder to the repository root.
3. Go to Settings → Pages.
4. Select `Deploy from a branch`.
5. Choose `main` branch and `/root` folder.
6. Replace `YOUR-GITHUB-USERNAME` in `index.html`, `robots.txt`, and `sitemap.xml` with your GitHub username.

